OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRain spreads
OL,6,Fnortheast through the evening, heavy
OL,7,Ffor a time. Becoming dry overnight
OL,8,Fwith some clear spells in the east but
OL,9,Fstaying cloudy in the southwest and
OL,10,Fover Southern Uplands.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FQuite cloudy to start but
OL,13,Fthis breaking up through the morning.
OL,14,FStaying dry and warm with prolonged
OL,15,Fbright or hazy sunny spells through
OL,16,Fthe day.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
