OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FWarm
OL,6,Ffrom Sunday to Tuesday with mostly
OL,7,Fbright or sunny spells, but generally
OL,8,Fcloudier in the southwest,
OL,9,Fparticularly on Sunday.
